&lt;li&gt;Internal mentor and cross-departmental buddy program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Friendly and inclusive workplace culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefits and Growth listed above may vary based on the country of your employment and the nature of your employment with Datadog.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
